headline: Palantir, Two Other Defense Names Head Toward Wins After Volatile Industry Week
summary: Palantir stock undercut its 50-day moving average on Thursday. Aerospace and defense names Howmet and Rocket Lab also fell.

headline: Why Howmet (HWM) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of aerospace and defense company Howmet (NYSE:HWM) jumped 3.3% in the morning session after Baird raised its price target on the company to $310 from $225 while keeping an Outperform rating.
